<p>The code is instructions written for computers to follow. But a human needs to be able to comprehend it. I think again about my English teacher. Heâ€™d tell me I was trying to work too many metaphors into my essays. There was a lot of stretching to make my writing fit the metaphors. Writing clever does not always translate to clear communication.</p>

